description: This Chainlink VRF top 15% score Gatinho purrs with a rating of 46, and a multiplier of 3x. It has a total score of 138, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are 1 for North, 2 for East, Nine Lives for South, and 2 for West. Gatinho has the personality suit of punter. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random packs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Gatinho [138 Votes, Top 15% Score]
